These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, action
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, lacrosse
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, roller
1. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
2. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
3. the person watching action movies is the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | sprite  | almond-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | epic   |
| Sport         | lacrosse | parkour |
| Transport     | trike | roller    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: lemon, banana
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, sports
2 different pets are kept: bird, mouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, taxi
1. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching satire movies is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person eating banana is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | lemon     | banana |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | satire  |
| Pet           | mouse         | bird     |
| Transport     | helicopter   | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, software-developer
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, dog
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the software-developer##1
3. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | lemonade     | milk |
| Job         | software-developer | mechanic    |
| Pet         | guinea-pig         | dog        |
| Transport   | tram         | jet-ski    |

