.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  photographer, journalist
There are 2 different nationalities: french, pakistani
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an even position##4
2. the pakistani is on the far left or far right##3
3. the journalist is the french##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | journalist | photographer    |
| Nationality   | french       | pakistani |
| Pet           | goldfish         | goat    |
| Sport         | baseball    | ice-hockey   |

